<TEXT>
<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Recapping:
</P>
<P>
   The following were eliminated from tonight's NYTNS budgets:
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-STARR (Washington)
</P>
<P>
   POLITICAL-BRIEFING (Undated)
</P>
<P>
   CRASH-INQUIRY (Undated)
</P>
<P>
   ANTITERROR-U.S. (Undated)
</P>
<P>
   JAPAN-U.S. (San Francisco)
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service.
</P>
