<HEADLINE>
LIST OF PASSENGERS AND CREW KILLED IN SWISSAIR CRASH 
</HEADLINE>
  (lh) 
 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Following is a list of 215 passengers and 14 crew members killed
