u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBN-PREVIEW-PICKS-NYT     09-05 0229
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FBN-PREVIEW-PICKS-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
NEW YORK TIMES SPORTS STAFF NFL '98 PREDICTIONS 
</HEADLINE>
  (jt) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Gerald Eskenazi:
</P>
<P>
   NFC East _ Washington
</P>
<P>
   NFC Central _ Green Bay
</P>
<P>
   NFC West _ San Francisco
</P>
<P>
   Conference champion _ Green Bay
</P>
<P>
