<SLUG> BC-WALKING-BOOKS-REVIEW-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TAKE A HIKE! CAN'T YOU SEE I'M READING? 
</HEADLINE>
  (The Week in Review) 
(duplication warning: also sent with `a' code) 
